NAME
	myHTTPd - run a simple HTTP server

SYNOPSIS
	./myHTTPd

DESCRIPTION
	This program run a simple HTTP server that handle GET request (but not
	execute CGI file). You can use it for create your own server and explore it
	with your favorite web brower.

	For run this program need ENVIRONEMENT VARIABLE (marked * are mandatory):
	*	LISTEN_IP:	contains the IP of the server

	*	LISTEN_PORT:	contains the port where the server should accept connexion

		ROOT_DIR:	the root directory of the server. If not set the root directory
				will be the current directory.
	
	GET request can only done on regular file.

INSTALL
	./autogen
	./configure
	make

TEST

